Patch Set 5: Code-Review-1

Yeah. You have to remove these files from your commit.

Please, do the following:

1.Reset locale files

git reset HEAD^ glance/locale/en_US/LC_MESSAGES/glance.po
git reset HEAD^ glance/locale/glance.pot

2. Amend your changes

git commit --amend

3. Send it for review

git review

Thanks in advance and good luck :)
